{"prompt": "Craft an online presence for a gourmet chocolate shop. The design should be luxurious, featuring a creamy yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Chocolatier Elegance</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f5f5dc; /* Creamy yellow */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, #f5f5dc, #e0d8b0); /* Creamy yellow gradient */\n            color: #4a2c2a; /* Dark chocolate brown */\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            background-color: #e0d8b0; /* Lighter creamy yellow */\n        }\n        nav a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: #4a2c2a;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #a0522d; /* Sienna brown for hover */\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #4a2c2a;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n        }\n        .intro-section {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n        .intro-section p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n        .products-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        .product-item {\n            text-align: center;\n            border: 1px solid #e0d8b0;\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            background-color: #fdfaf6;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .product-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .product-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n        .product-item h3 {\n            color: #4a2c2a;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n        .product-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n            color: #666;\n        }\n        .price {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #a0522d;\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n            display: block;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            background-color: #e0d8b0;\n            color: #4a2c2a;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Chocolatier Elegance</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#products\">Our Chocolates</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"intro-section\">\n            <h2>Experience Pure Indulgence</h2>\n            <p>\n                At Chocolatier Elegance, we craft exquisite chocolates using the finest cocoa beans and artisanal techniques. Each bite is a journey of rich flavors and unparalleled luxury.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"products\">\n            <h2>Our Signature Creations</h2>\n            <div class=\"products-grid\">\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/f5f5dc/4a2c2a?text=Dark+Truffles\" alt=\"Dark Chocolate Truffles\">\n                    <h3>Midnight Truffles</h3>\n                    <p>Intensely rich dark chocolate ganache, dusted with cocoa powder.</p>\n                    <span class=\"price\">$18.00</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/f5f5dc/4a2c2a?text=Milk+Caramels\" alt=\"Milk Chocolate Caramels\">\n                    <h3>Salted Caramel Delights</h3>\n                    <p>Velvety milk chocolate enrobing a smooth, sea-salted caramel.</p>\n                    <span class=\"price\">$16.00</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/f5f5dc/4a2c2a?text=Fruit+Bonbons\" alt=\"Assorted Fruit Bonbons\">\n                    <h3>Exotic Fruit Bonbons</h3>\n                    <p>A vibrant selection of fruit-infused ganaches in a delicate shell.</p>\n                    <span class=\"price\">$20.00</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/f5f5dc/4a2c2a?text=Almond+Bark\" alt=\"Almond Bark\">\n                    <h3>Toasted Almond Bark</h3>\n                    <p>Crisp dark chocolate layered with perfectly toasted almonds.</p>\n                    <span class=\"price\">$15.00</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;\">\n            <h2>Visit Us or Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>\n                We invite you to explore our full collection in-store or order online for a taste of pure bliss.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <strong>Address:</strong> 123 Chocolate Lane, Sweet City, SC 54321\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <strong>Email:</strong> info@chocolatier-elegance.com\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890\n            </p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Chocolatier Elegance. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}